    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Edinburgh, Scotland,</name>
                    <date when="1890-07-31">July 31, 1890<ptr target="med.00888_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>My Dear Walt&#8212;</salute>
            </opener>

            <p>Again I salute you. I wish I had been at the birth-day fest<ptr target="loc.07350_n2"
                />, and heard the beauteous words of my friend Bob. Ingersoll<ptr target="n0839"/>
                about you.</p>

            <p>We shall leave here soon for New York[.]</p>

            <closer>
                <salute>Ever yours</salute>
                <signed>John Swinton</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
